name: Monopoly Monstrosity // Crypto Wook x Marc Craig
description: The first official collab piece I’ve done with another artist in the space other than Marc Craig for #HenThousand. You can find his work at marccraig.xyz & Twitter: @marccraigart. Remaining editions will be burned in roughly 24 hours. We are rewarding collectors of 20 editions their own unique 1/1 portrait collab made by Crypto Wook x Marc Craig that will be minted and sent directly to them. Find out more details on Twitter: @crypto_wook
